[
    {
        "text": "(knife chopping)",
        "start": 0.383,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(happy music)",
        "start": 1.216,
        "duration": 2.394
    },
    {
        "text": "- Hi everybody!",
        "start": 3.61,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's make something sweet;\nsweet, cold, refreshing dessert.",
        "start": 4.85,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, we are going to\nmake Sikhye, Korean Sikhye.",
        "start": 9.57,
        "duration": 3.51
    },
    {
        "text": "Sikhye is rice punch,\nbecause it made with rice.",
        "start": 13.08,
        "duration": 3.049
    },
    {
        "text": "See, we can make anything with rice!",
        "start": 16.129,
        "duration": 4.001
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a very popular\ndessert among Koreans.",
        "start": 20.13,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever we have some special occasions,",
        "start": 23.61,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "always, we make this Sikhye.",
        "start": 26.26,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Because, we eat a lot of\ndelicious food, after that,",
        "start": 28.24,
        "duration": 3.424
    },
    {
        "text": "our stomach is kind of, it'll\nfeel uncomfortable, too full.",
        "start": 31.664,
        "duration": 4.146
    },
    {
        "text": "This rice punch, you just drink this,",
        "start": 35.81,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "and then all digests quickly.",
        "start": 38.16,
        "duration": 2.513
    },
    {
        "text": "Also, tasty, because we make\nthis with barley malt powder,",
        "start": 41.612,
        "duration": 4.401
    },
    {
        "text": "the malty flavor,\naftertaste is amazing, so good.",
        "start": 46.013,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We call this yeotkiereum-garu,\nbarley malt powder.",
        "start": 52.142,
        "duration": 2.278
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, I will just make\n kind of a slush style.",
        "start": 54.42,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "It's perfect for summer weather!",
        "start": 57.79,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "This is eight ounce,",
        "start": 60.14,
        "duration": 1.353
    },
    {
        "text": "then I will add 14 cups water.",
        "start": 63.43,
        "duration": 2.603
    },
    {
        "text": "We got to mix this very well.",
        "start": 72.81,
        "duration": 2.86
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to wait until this\npowder is all sunk on the bottom,",
        "start": 75.67,
        "duration": 4.75
    },
    {
        "text": "then we need to get only its clear water,",
        "start": 80.42,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "clear malty water we need there.",
        "start": 83.42,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Before filming this, two hours\nbefore, I mixed this one here.",
        "start": 85.87,
        "duration": 4.703
    },
    {
        "text": "This bowl is just clear liquid,\nyou can see the difference.",
        "start": 91.721,
        "duration": 3.252
    },
    {
        "text": "Nobody can touch it  now,\nbecause it's very important;",
        "start": 96.48,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "if you touch and shake it,\nall will be mixed again, oh my!",
        "start": 99.52,
        "duration": 4.473
    },
    {
        "text": "Just my time, two hours,\nI have to wait again!",
        "start": 103.993,
        "duration": 3.637
    },
    {
        "text": "(laughs)",
        "start": 107.63,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "So how important it is.",
        "start": 109.2,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to save this for later.",
        "start": 110.89,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I will make rice.",
        "start": 113.79,
        "duration": 2.213
    },
    {
        "text": "One cup.",
        "start": 117.48,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's wash.",
        "start": 120.86,
        "duration": 1.054
    },
    {
        "text": "(faucet running)",
        "start": 121.914,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "And rinse.",
        "start": 127.4,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "And change water.",
        "start": 130.16,
        "duration": 1.403
    },
    {
        "text": "In my last rinse, I will pour\nout water, as much as I can.",
        "start": 137.34,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "3/4 cup water.",
        "start": 144.41,
        "duration": 1.713
    },
    {
        "text": "1/2 a cup.",
        "start": 146.968,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "1/4 cup.",
        "start": 149.309,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "You see, not much water.",
        "start": 151.938,
        "duration": 1.819
    },
    {
        "text": "Press the button, and make rice.",
        "start": 157.91,
        "duration": 4.99
    },
    {
        "text": "There is a little science\ninvolved making this.",
        "start": 162.9,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "Barley malt has enzyme called amylase.",
        "start": 166.11,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "When amylase is meeting starch from rice,",
        "start": 170.23,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "the starch turns into\nsugar, sweet thing.",
        "start": 173.61,
        "duration": 4.25
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, you make rice,",
        "start": 177.86,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "and just mix it with this malty water,",
        "start": 179.67,
        "duration": 3.21
    },
    {
        "text": "then suddenly it makes\na sweet drink!",
        "start": 182.88,
        "duration": 3.71
    },
    {
        "text": "That's amazing, isn't it?",
        "start": 186.59,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "My rice is done!",
        "start": 188.04,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's check it out.",
        "start": 189.56,
        "duration": 0.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh wow.",
        "start": 193.033,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Each grain of rice is cooked and firm.",
        "start": 195.27,
        "duration": 3.383
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what we need.",
        "start": 200.4,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "So I'm going to really\ncarefully just pour out this.",
        "start": 201.6,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Slowly, slowly like this.",
        "start": 206.819,
        "duration": 0.864
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you see there on the bottom?",
        "start": 210.94,
        "duration": 3.227
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like mud.",
        "start": 214.167,
        "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
        "text": "I will just stop this,",
        "start": 217.21,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "because I don't want to\nmake cloudy Sikyhe.",
        "start": 219.67,
        "duration": 3.737
    },
    {
        "text": "This is around 11 cups malty water.",
        "start": 224.559,
        "duration": 3.431
    },
    {
        "text": "And then now, close.",
        "start": 227.99,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "You need to set to warm.",
        "start": 231.3,
        "duration": 2.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Keep warm, can you see?",
        "start": 233.41,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "And press this.",
        "start": 235.25,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "I still like to use this.",
        "start": 237.98,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "This is four cups of water,",
        "start": 239.95,
        "duration": 2.623
    },
    {
        "text": "the color is a little grayish.",
        "start": 244.094,
        "duration": 4.066
    },
    {
        "text": "That's it!",
        "start": 252.44,
        "duration": 0.94
    },
    {
        "text": "I don't have to worry about this sikhye!",
        "start": 253.38,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to let it\nferment for four hours,",
        "start": 256.44,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "and four hours later I will check it out.",
        "start": 259.16,
        "duration": 2.657
    },
    {
        "text": "The rice is going to be light,\nand color will be changed to white.",
        "start": 261.817,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Grains of rice should be floating.",
        "start": 267.09,
        "duration": 2.17
    },
    {
        "text": "Meanwhile, I'm not going\nto touch this.",
        "start": 269.26,
        "duration": 2.83
    },
    {
        "text": "Four hours later it'll\nbe nicely separated.",
        "start": 272.09,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "So see you in four hours!",
        "start": 275.17,
        "duration": 2.982
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat guitar music)",
        "start": 278.152,
        "duration": 3.167
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm back, four hours later.",
        "start": 292.4,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's check it out!",
        "start": 295.14,
        "duration": 1.183
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow, look at this!",
        "start": 299.42,
        "duration": 1.463
    },
    {
        "text": "This rice is floating!",
        "start": 301.97,
        "duration": 3.203
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, I'm going to transfer\nthis to my big pot.",
        "start": 307.0,
        "duration": 4.493
    },
    {
        "text": "Look at this color, gorgeous, beautiful.",
        "start": 321.51,
        "duration": 3.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Delicious looking and it smells really good.",
        "start": 324.94,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "The sediment is sunk\non the bottom.",
        "start": 330.137,
        "duration": 4.136
    },
    {
        "text": "Pour this, just the clear\nliquid, very slowly slowly.",
        "start": 336.397,
        "duration": 3.163
    },
    {
        "text": "Around three cups.",
        "start": 342.27,
        "duration": 1.433
    },
    {
        "text": "I will boil this really\nvigorously, and then, turn off.",
        "start": 348.51,
        "duration": 4.19
    },
    {
        "text": "That's Sikhye!",
        "start": 352.7,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "And this leftover sediment is",
        "start": 354.06,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "not delicious anymore.",
        "start": 357.21,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "All the malt flavor was infused,\nso throw it away.",
        "start": 358.95,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's heat up over high heat.",
        "start": 366.27,
        "duration": 2.133
    },
    {
        "text": "It's really boiling now.",
        "start": 370.12,
        "duration": 1.713
    },
    {
        "text": "Turn off.",
        "start": 385.9,
        "duration": 0.923
    },
    {
        "text": "This tastes just subtly sweet,",
        "start": 389.17,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "we  usually add some sugar here.",
        "start": 391.86,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "You can taste this, \"Oh, this is good.\"",
        "start": 394.49,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "and then, don't add any sugar.",
        "start": 397.19,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "But I will add one cup sugar.",
        "start": 399.07,
        "duration": 2.123
    },
    {
        "text": "Ever since I was young,\nmy grandmother, my mom,",
        "start": 415.41,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "when they made Sikyhe,  hot\nSikhye was so delicious.",
        "start": 418.55,
        "duration": 4.543
    },
    {
        "text": "So we were always eating\na little bit to taste.",
        "start": 423.093,
        "duration": 3.277
    },
    {
        "text": "You can serve it hot or cold.",
        "start": 426.37,
        "duration": 2.003
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, yummy, yummy!",
        "start": 431.28,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Serve hot or cold,\nbut we usually serve cold.",
        "start": 433.14,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "The rice will keep\nfermenting in this water.",
        "start": 437.61,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "As time goes by, the color\nis going to be more cloudy,",
        "start": 440.92,
        "duration": 3.71
    },
    {
        "text": "or grayish.",
        "start": 444.63,
        "duration": 1.37
    },
    {
        "text": "So we usually separate rice",
        "start": 446.0,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "and Sikhye water.",
        "start": 449.47,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "How I'm doing this? I will strain it.",
        "start": 452.37,
        "duration": 2.883
    },
    {
        "text": "Then let's rinse this in cold water.",
        "start": 468.12,
        "duration": 2.804
    },
    {
        "text": "(faucet running)",
        "start": 470.924,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Just soak this in cold water.",
        "start": 484.886,
        "duration": 3.907
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me taste my Sikhye!",
        "start": 497.77,
        "duration": 1.467
    },
    {
        "text": "Ah, so good~",
        "start": 503.458,
        "duration": 1.405
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, what I'm going to do\nis just let it cool down.",
        "start": 505.88,
        "duration": 3.55
    },
    {
        "text": "This Sikhye water, and Sikhye rice,",
        "start": 509.43,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "keep these separately in the refrigerator,",
        "start": 512.71,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "so whenever you serve this,",
        "start": 516.01,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "you can ladle some Sikhye\nwater and scoop some rice.",
        "start": 518.1,
        "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the way that we serve Sikhye",
        "start": 522.38,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "so that the color is not\ngoing to change, and pretty,",
        "start": 525.35,
        "duration": 3.73
    },
    {
        "text": "rice color is always white,\nbeautiful and floating.",
        "start": 529.08,
        "duration": 4.54
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll just keep eating this again.",
        "start": 533.62,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "The flavor is really good,\nsweet, but not that sweet.",
        "start": 541.8,
        "duration": 4.343
    },
    {
        "text": "This is total, about 14 to 15 cups.",
        "start": 557.79,
        "duration": 3.173
    },
    {
        "text": "When it's cooled down,  cover.",
        "start": 562.83,
        "duration": 2.973
    },
    {
        "text": "Now I'm going to make slush.",
        "start": 571.78,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "To show you how to make slush,\nI had to make another batch.",
        "start": 574.28,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I froze it for around five hours.",
        "start": 579.78,
        "duration": 2.98
    },
    {
        "text": "I will bring it, but before that,",
        "start": 582.76,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "I will just give you an idea for garnish.",
        "start": 585.47,
        "duration": 3.161
    },
    {
        "text": "You remember,  jujube?",
        "start": 588.631,
        "duration": 2.311
    },
    {
        "text": "With jujubes, I made these\nflowers. How you make this?",
        "start": 590.942,
        "duration": 3.151
    },
    {
        "text": "Use your knife and just cut around it,",
        "start": 594.093,
        "duration": 4.787
    },
    {
        "text": "you can feel the seed\ninside, and just cut around,",
        "start": 598.88,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "until the seed is coming out.",
        "start": 604.46,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "You see? Seed.",
        "start": 610.201,
        "duration": 0.962
    },
    {
        "text": "And then you can just roll\nit, roll it up tightly,",
        "start": 612.25,
        "duration": 4.41
    },
    {
        "text": "and squeeze,",
        "start": 619.26,
        "duration": 1.203
    },
    {
        "text": "because the inside is\nsticky, you can do this.",
        "start": 622.69,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Just like a glue, you know?",
        "start": 626.89,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "It's  jujube flower.",
        "start": 637.82,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "This way we make this, I made some here.",
        "start": 639.46,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "And also, these are pine nuts.",
        "start": 642.92,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Pine nut  in Sikyhe, is always very beautiful and tasty.",
        "start": 645.12,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "When we add pine nuts, we\nalways remove the tips.",
        "start": 649.02,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "See, this is the tip!",
        "start": 653.38,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "You can take off the tip.",
        "start": 655.53,
        "duration": 3.153
    },
    {
        "text": "Actually there is a little tiny hole inside,",
        "start": 659.6,
        "duration": 4.13
    },
    {
        "text": "so you should be able to do like this.",
        "start": 665.898,
        "duration": 2.542
    },
    {
        "text": "What does it look like?",
        "start": 668.44,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "It looks like a match! (laughs)",
        "start": 670.65,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "We usually make this with pine needles.",
        "start": 672.94,
        "duration": 4.483
    },
    {
        "text": "(laughs)",
        "start": 677.423,
        "duration": 1.977
    },
    {
        "text": "I just kept this in the refrigerator, so it's very cold.",
        "start": 679.4,
        "duration": 4.443
    },
    {
        "text": "You see, just half is frozen.",
        "start": 686.369,
        "duration": 2.744
    },
    {
        "text": "This is slush!",
        "start": 691.372,
        "duration": 2.211
    },
    {
        "text": "In the summertime, it is awesome,",
        "start": 695.92,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "you can make slush with all\nthese two jars, and use for a big party,",
        "start": 698.21,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "you can serve this way for several people.",
        "start": 703.551,
        "duration": 4.419
    },
    {
        "text": "I also made granita with it.",
        "start": 707.97,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Have you ever heard of granita?",
        "start": 710.81,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Using your fork, and then\njust scratch, scratch.",
        "start": 712.34,
        "duration": 3.453
    },
    {
        "text": "Add some  rice and mix it together.",
        "start": 724.578,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Jujube, pine nuts.",
        "start": 735.03,
        "duration": 2.263
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me taste!",
        "start": 739.42,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm so excited about this Sikhye slush!",
        "start": 740.253,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow, almost too cold, too cold.",
        "start": 751.254,
        "duration": 2.926
    },
    {
        "text": "My teeth are frozen!",
        "start": 754.18,
        "duration": 1.553
    },
    {
        "text": "It tastes cold, refreshing, and sweet,",
        "start": 758.33,
        "duration": 3.77
    },
    {
        "text": "and the aftertaste is\nkind of a malt flavor,",
        "start": 762.1,
        "duration": 3.814
    },
    {
        "text": "that's really great.",
        "start": 765.914,
        "duration": 1.806
    },
    {
        "text": "All the starch from the rice is gone, so",
        "start": 767.72,
        "duration": 3.51
    },
    {
        "text": "the texture is like sponge.",
        "start": 771.23,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "The taste is really unique, if\nyou have never tasted Sikhye,",
        "start": 773.31,
        "duration": 4.09
    },
    {
        "text": "you got to make homemade Sikhye.",
        "start": 777.4,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Sikhye is loved by all Koreans,",
        "start": 779.36,
        "duration": 2.957
    },
    {
